{"tid":1663974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報文章斥段崇智公開信偏頗　只談被捕學生聲音","createTime":"2019-10-19T18:12:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T00:11:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ad54548d282705979fc1aaf27892986896635155","tid":1663974,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T18:12:15.000Z","msg":"內地人民日報發表評論文章，質疑香港中大校長段崇智日前發表的公開信，內容只有「被捕學生的聲音」，卻讀不出該有的客觀、慎重，反而更多感到是偏頗和臆測。<br />\n<br />\n文章認為，在沒有經過權威調查、充分了解各方情況的前提下，只是把被捕學生的單方面說法呈現出來，質疑是否能拼出完整的事實、是否能體現出真正的客觀、公正、是否可能帶偏輿論，進而干擾獨立的檢控和審判。<br />\n<br />\n文章批評，公開信的價值，在於提供一個反思的契機，倘若教師甚至深受尊重的大學校長也「隨波逐流」，不辨是非、不講對錯，對極端激進的觀點乃至暴力一味縱容，那不是真正愛護年輕人，而是在親手毀了他們的未來。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487176-20191020.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487176-20191020.htm&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=5c7cb7c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1487176-20191020.htm&h=91b0f1b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1487176-20191020.htm</a>"},{"pid":"efbbac0658a2a14a7ec744a5593c1c5d640eec4b","tid":1663974,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T18:12:24.000Z","msg":"【1020 尖咀見】真。遊行指南參考<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/aksjJwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aksjJwU</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e2fa8e5bb794771a8098ad576a543053d0c866","tid":1663974,"uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T18:12:24.000Z","msg":"聲援段崇智<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" cl